{"tid":637612,"cid":1,"subCid":0,"title":"未有電話之前 大家記唔記得以前起身第一件事係做咩？","createTime":"2018-04-22T03:18:05.000Z","updateTime":"2018-04-22T03:34:26.000Z","uid":114576,"like":0,"dislike":1,"uniUserReply":6,"replies":[{"pid":"b03ce36f4f2f0c2a07b3754192f57bec170b1ea0","tid":637612,"uid":114576,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-04-22T03:18:05.000Z","msg":"我發現每朝起身，就算隻眼好攰，都要爬起身禁電話，睇下有邊個揾你 ，發生咩事咁。但我已經醒唔起係冇電話既年代，起身第一件事唔洗諗有冇人搵你，唔洗理世界發生咩事，個感覺係點。因為唔開電視根本唔會知，以前到底係唔係會賴少啲床，多啲即刻起身去同屋企人傾下計、一齊睇下電視咁呢？<br />\n<br />\n想知大家會做啲咩<img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/26.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"3d81fdfe21cccce0f824d257ed8c955e574cc25d","tid":637612,"uid":15394,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-04-22T03:19:43.000Z","msg":"摸一摸自己碌鳩有幾硬⋯⋯⋯⋯⋯⋯⋯"},{"pid":"ed70d91edaccf16a28eee492b8c322585c010739","tid":637612,"uid":48222,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"3d81fdfe21cccce0f824d257ed8c955e574cc25d","tid":637612,"uid":15394,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-04-22T03:19:43.000Z","msg":"摸一摸自己碌鳩有幾硬⋯⋯⋯⋯⋯⋯⋯"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-04-22T03:22:51.000Z","msg":"即係而家硬唔到<img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/08.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"e7f955275a2c259c0a80a03c90dfef32f4a5be5b","tid":637612,"uid":116530,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-04-22T03:30:45.000Z","msg":"擘大隻眼"},{"pid":"6520cf0f4f877031301590197ba1e337a1922a2d","tid":637612,"uid":13281,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-04-22T03:32:17.000Z","msg":"郁一郁隻mouse著moon再去刷牙<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"0bb327cd5c5239c3cd38be3ef332025a9274520b","tid":637612,"uid":83798,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-04-22T03:34:26.000Z","msg":"開電腦"}]}